displayName: Captain Melena's House of the Pirate Crew

events.name: ピラタ海賊団船長メレーナ

parameters:
Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Thank you for
coming, my saviors!
Clea: Weren't you supposed to be caught by the guards?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: In this world,
many things can be solved with money.

Priestess Sophia: Are you saying that we were called here
for a troublesome matter that cannot be solved with just
money?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: She's a sharp
young lady, I want you to take a look at her.
Thief Nora: The crown... it's made of bones!?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: We found a
suspicious ship at night and decided to board it to steal
the treasure.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: There was no
one on the ship... It was too eerie, so I only stole this
crown.

Pirate Captain Melena: After that, strange things started
happening. The crew members began getting sick and injured,
and in the end, they were attacked by monsters.

Mage Relm: L-Let's refuse this request... Don't you all
feel it...? There's something strange about this crown.

Mage Relm: I've seen many things at the academy, but I have
to say, I've never seen something as ominous as this
before...

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: I consulted
with the mages, but they gave me the same response. This
crown is cursed and brings misfortune to its owner.

Pirate Captain Melena: It seems that the main god, Sol, has
bestowed upon me a judgment that is not a life to be proud
of.
Clea: Let us take on this task.

Priestess Sophia: If Clea-chan has decided, then I will
follow...

Clea: I won't refuse the request I've taken on. That's the
way of the adventurer's guild, Futera.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: I'm grateful,
miss...!
Thief Nora: Everyone, there's someone outside...!

Pirate Captain Melena: O-Oh... Is something going to happen
again...!?
Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Who are you!
Clea: Do we know you? What are you doing here?

Tailor Neuro: I happened to find you guys! It seems like
you're sticking your noses into something interesting!

Tailor Neuro: Take me with you too! If I get inspired, I
can make swimsuits!

Mage Relm: I guess there's no helping it...! As the genius
mage, I'll take care of things properly!

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: I'll leave the
details to you guys. What I want is for you to return the
crown to the treasure chest on the ship.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: I'll be at the
dock, so please talk to me when you're ready.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Thank you for
coming, my saviors!
Clea: What kind of request is it this time?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: Ladies, do you
know about the Island of Prostitution?

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: It's a
paradise for men and a land of despair for women. I sent
them there for work, but they still haven't returned.

Clea: I understand the request, but is it a place that we
can easily access?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, there's someone in Mucos who is
good at this kind of thing.

Pirate Captain Melena: I used to have a falling out with
the organization that runs Mucos, so I can't enter the
Island of Prostitution.

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: They may be
fools, but I want you to somehow rescue them.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Pirate Captain Melena of the Pirata Pirates: He may be a
fool, but he's an important subordinate. I'm counting on
you.

Captain Melena of the Pirate Crew: I made those idiots from
the Prostitution Island clean the ship for three months.
Well, I'm glad they're still alive, though.
Pirate Crew Member Wishing you success!

Pirate Crew Member: Thanks to you, we've been saved. We
will cooperate with the Adventurer's Guild!

Pirate Shop Clerk: I'm sorry! I cannot provide you with any
items!

Pirate Shop Clerk: Oh... please take a look at our
treasured items.
